arning in this asset, as I am planning on switching to the CS + Stats major. I believe that my experience with analyzing economic and financial data will help me to contribute more creative ideas when it comes to implementing new strategies for trading with stocks. Finally, I‚Äôve also gained some leadership skills from the activities I was a part of in high school, and I plan on using those to foster better communication with my peers on the different teams of Quant.' , 'I would like a chance to gain more experience and connections within the quantitative trading industry, as it is one that I am very interested in as a potential career field. I believe the projects that I would work on as a part of Quant will give me greater experience when applying to internships at trading firms, which would also give me a greater capacity to develop independent projects dealing with the material. Furthermore, I believe that the collaborative projects that I will be a part of will help me develop better communication skills that I can use in the future. I want to be part of an environment where my peers will help me foster better programming skills for the future, as well as one that I feel comfortable in with people of like-minded interests.');   
